      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Restless Swamp",
        "Client": "Guild Master Hojo",
        "Description": "One of our scouts tracking\r\na \u003CCOL RED\u003EJyuratodus\u003C/COL\u003E has gone missing\r\nin the Flooded Forest. If you\r\nwould hunt the beast so that\r\nit is safe enough to dispatch\r\na search party, it would be much\r\nappreciated. Now, hop to it-to it!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le marais agit\u00E9",
        "Client": "Hojo le Ma\u00EEtre de la Guilde",
        "Description": "Un de nos \u00E9claireurs s\u0027est perdu\r\ndans la For\u00EAt inond\u00E9e en traquant\r\nun \u003CCOL RED\u003EJyuratodus\u003C/COL\u003E. Nous comptons sur\r\ntoi pour chasser ce monstre\r\nafin que nous puissions envoyer\r\nune \u00E9quipe de secours \u00E0\r\nsa recherche.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "La palude irrequieta",
        "Client": "Hojo il capo della Gilda",
        "Description": "Uno dei nostri ricercatori che\r\ninseguiva un \u003CCOL RED\u003EJyuratodus\u003C/COL\u003E \u00E8\r\nscomparso nella Foresta\r\ninondata. Ci aiuteresti molto\r\nse lo cacciassi, cos\u00EC la zona\r\nsar\u00E0 sicura e potremo inviare\r\nuna squadra di ricerca. Vai!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Jyuratodus",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Der ruhelose Sumpf",
        "Client": "Gildenmeister Hojo",
        "Description": "Einer unserer Sp\u00E4her, der im\r\nFlutwald einen \u003CCOL RED\u003EJyuratodus\u003C/COL\u003E ver-\r\nfolgt hat, wird vermisst. Wenn\r\ndu die Bestie jagen w\u00FCrdest,\r\ndamit wir einen Suchtrupp\r\nentsenden k\u00F6nnen, w\u00E4re ich dir\r\nsehr verbunden. Dann mal los!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Jyuratodus.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "El pantano turbulento",
        "Client": "Hojo el maestro del gremio",
        "Description": "Han visto un \u003CCOL RED\u003EJyuratodus\u003C/COL\u003E en\r\nel Bosque inundado, y se ha\r\nperdido un investigador del\r\ngremio tambi\u00E9n all\u00ED. Necesito\r\nque lo caces para despachar\r\nuna partida de busca. \u00A1A ello!",
